{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"I want to start out by asking you to think back to when you were a kid,"},{"time":2000,"text":"playing with blocks."},{"time":4000,"text":"As you figured out how to reach out and grasp,"},{"time":6000,"text":"pick them up and move them around,"},{"time":8000,"text":"you were actually learning how to think and solve problems"},{"time":10000,"text":"by understanding and manipulating spatial relationships."},{"time":13000,"text":"Spatial reasoning is deeply connected"},{"time":16000,"text":"to how we understand a lot of the world around us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":18000,"text":"So, as a computer scientist"},{"time":20000,"text":"inspired by this utility of our interactions with physical objects --"},{"time":23000,"text":"along with my adviser Pattie, and my collaborator Jeevan Kalanithi --"},{"time":27000,"text":"I started to wonder -- what if when we used a computer,"},{"time":30000,"text":"instead of having this one mouse cursor that was a like a digital fingertip"},{"time":33000,"text":"moving around a flat desktop,"},{"time":35000,"text":"what if we could reach in with both hands and grasp information physically,"},{"time":39000,"text":"arranging it the way we wanted?"},{"time":41000,"text":"This question was so compelling that we decided to explore the answer,"},{"time":44000,"text":"by building Siftables."}]},{"cues":[{"time":46000,"text":"In a nutshell, a Siftable is an interactive computer"},{"time":49000,"text":"the size of a cookie."},{"time":51000,"text":"They're able to be moved around by hand,"},{"time":53000,"text":"they can sense each other, they can sense their motion,"},{"time":55000,"text":"and they have a screen and a wireless radio."},{"time":58000,"text":"Most importantly, they're physical,"},{"time":60000,"text":"so like the blocks, you can move them just by reaching out and grasping."},{"time":63000,"text":"And Siftables are an example of a new ecosystem"},{"time":66000,"text":"of tools for manipulating digital information."},{"time":68000,"text":"And as these tools become more physical,"},{"time":71000,"text":"more aware of their motion, aware of each other,"},{"time":73000,"text":"and aware of the nuance of how we move them,"},{"time":75000,"text":"we can start to explore some new and fun interaction styles."},{"time":78000,"text":"So, I'm going to start with some simple examples."}]},{"cues":[{"time":80000,"text":"This Siftable is configured to show video,"},{"time":83000,"text":"and if I tilt it in one direction, it'll roll the video this way;"},{"time":85000,"text":"if I tilt it the other way it rolls it backwards."},{"time":88000,"text":"And these interactive portraits are aware of each other."},{"time":91000,"text":"So if I put them next to each other, they get interested."},{"time":94000,"text":"If they get surrounded, they notice that too,"},{"time":98000,"text":"they might get a little flustered."},{"time":100000,"text":"And they can also sense their motion and tilt."}]},{"cues":[{"time":104000,"text":"One of the interesting implications on interaction, we started to realize,"},{"time":109000,"text":"was that we could use everyday gestures on data,"},{"time":111000,"text":"like pouring a color the way we might pour a liquid."},{"time":114000,"text":"So in this case, we've got three Siftables configured to be paint buckets"},{"time":118000,"text":"and I can use them to pour color into that central one,"},{"time":121000,"text":"where they get mixed."},{"time":123000,"text":"If we overshoot, we can pour a little bit back."}]},{"cues":[{"time":127000,"text":"There are also some neat possibilities for education,"},{"time":130000,"text":"like language, math and logic games"},{"time":132000,"text":"where we want to give people the ability to try things quickly,"},{"time":134000,"text":"and view the results immediately."},{"time":137000,"text":"So here I'm --"},{"time":139000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":141000,"text":"This is a Fibonacci sequence that I'm making with a simple equation program."}]},{"cues":[{"time":145000,"text":"Here we have a word game that's kind of like a mash-up between Scrabble and Boggle."},{"time":149000,"text":"Basically, in every round"},{"time":151000,"text":"you get a randomly assigned letter on each Siftable,"},{"time":153000,"text":"and as you try to make words it checks against a dictionary."},{"time":156000,"text":"Then, after about 30 seconds, it reshuffles,"},{"time":159000,"text":"and you have a new set of letters and new possibilities to try."}]},{"cues":[{"time":162000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":163000,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":164000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":166000,"text":"So these are some kids that came on a field trip to the Media Lab,"},{"time":168000,"text":"and I managed to get them to try it out, and shoot a video."},{"time":178000,"text":"They really loved it."},{"time":180000,"text":"And, one of the interesting things about this kind of application"},{"time":183000,"text":"is that you don't have to give people many instructions."},{"time":186000,"text":"All you have to say is, \"Make words,\""},{"time":188000,"text":"and they know exactly what to do."}]},{"cues":[{"time":190000,"text":"So here's another few people trying it out."},{"time":199000,"text":"That's our youngest beta tester, down there on the right."},{"time":204000,"text":"Turns out, all he wanted to do was to stack the Siftables up."},{"time":210000,"text":"So to him, they were just blocks."},{"time":214000,"text":"Now, this is an interactive cartoon application."},{"time":217000,"text":"And we wanted to build a learning tool for language learners."},{"time":222000,"text":"And this is Felix, actually."},{"time":225000,"text":"And he can bring new characters into the scene,"},{"time":227000,"text":"just by lifting the Siftables off the table that have that character shown on them."},{"time":231000,"text":"Here, he's bringing the sun out."}]},{"cues":[{"time":235000,"text":"Video: The sun is rising."}]},{"cues":[{"time":237000,"text":"David Merrill: Now he's brought a tractor into the scene."}]},{"cues":[{"time":241000,"text":"Video: The orange tractor."},{"time":243000,"text":"Good job! Yeah!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":246000,"text":"DM: So by shaking the Siftables and putting them next to each other"},{"time":249000,"text":"he can make the characters interact --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":251000,"text":"Video: Woof!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":252000,"text":"DM: inventing his own narrative."}]},{"cues":[{"time":254000,"text":"Video: Hello!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":255000,"text":"DM: It's an open-ended story,"},{"time":257000,"text":"and he gets to decide how it unfolds."}]},{"cues":[{"time":262000,"text":"Video: Fly away, cat."}]},{"cues":[{"time":270000,"text":"DM: So, the last example I have time to show you today"},{"time":273000,"text":"is a music sequencing and live performance tool"},{"time":275000,"text":"that we've built recently,"},{"time":277000,"text":"in which Siftables act as sounds"},{"time":280000,"text":"like lead, bass and drums."},{"time":282000,"text":"Each of these has four different variations,"},{"time":284000,"text":"you get to choose which one you want to use."},{"time":286000,"text":"And you can inject these sounds into a sequence"},{"time":289000,"text":"that you can assemble into the pattern that you want."},{"time":292000,"text":"And you inject it by just bumping up the sound Siftable against a sequence Siftable."},{"time":296000,"text":"There are effects that you can control live, like reverb and filter."},{"time":300000,"text":"You attach it to a particular sound and then tilt to adjust it."},{"time":303000,"text":"And then, overall effects like tempo and volume"},{"time":306000,"text":"that apply to the entire sequence."},{"time":308000,"text":"So let's have a look."}]},{"cues":[{"time":310000,"text":"Video: (Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":312000,"text":"DM: We'll start by putting a lead"},{"time":314000,"text":"into two sequence Siftables, arrange them into a series,"},{"time":319000,"text":"extend it, add a little more lead."},{"time":322000,"text":"Now I put a bass line in."}]},{"cues":[{"time":324000,"text":"Video: (Music)"},{"time":329000,"text":"DM: Now I'll put some percussion in."},{"time":331000,"text":"Video: (Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":336000,"text":"DM: And now I'll attach the filter to the drums, so I can control the effect live."}]},{"cues":[{"time":339000,"text":"Video: (Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":341000,"text":"DM: I can speed up the whole sequence"},{"time":343000,"text":"by tilting the tempo one way or the other."}]},{"cues":[{"time":346000,"text":"Video: (Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":348000,"text":"DM: And now I'll attach the filter to the bass for some more expression."}]},{"cues":[{"time":351000,"text":"Video: (Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":356000,"text":"DM: I can rearrange the sequence while it plays."},{"time":359000,"text":"So I don't have to plan it out in advance, but I can improvise,"},{"time":361000,"text":"making it longer or shorter as I go."},{"time":364000,"text":"And now, finally, I can fade the whole sequence out"},{"time":367000,"text":"using the volume Siftable, tilted to the left."}]},{"cues":[{"time":370000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":375000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":377000,"text":"So, as you can see,"},{"time":380000,"text":"my passion is for making new human-computer interfaces"},{"time":383000,"text":"that are a better match to the ways our brains and bodies work."},{"time":386000,"text":"And today, I had time to show you one point in this new design space,"},{"time":390000,"text":"and a few of the possibilities that we're working to bring out of the laboratory."},{"time":393000,"text":"So the thought I want to leave you with"},{"time":395000,"text":"is that we're on the cusp of this new generation of tools"},{"time":398000,"text":"for interacting with digital media"},{"time":401000,"text":"that are going to bring information into our world"},{"time":404000,"text":"on our terms."},{"time":406000,"text":"Thank you very much."},{"time":407000,"text":"I look forward to talking with all of you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":409000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}